| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2025-3032 — Recovery Inhibition (qilin)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: b8e20e63-c2c7-5d4b-a6bb-3bcfbb95ed25"
